item.title: CVE-2021-4208|2024-08-03T17:16:04.256Z -- unknown -- exportfeed%3A%20list%20woocommerce%20products%20on%20ebay%20store
item.description: The ExportFeed WordPress plugin through 2.0.1.0 does not sanitise and escape the product_id POST parameter before using it in a SQL statement, leading to a SQL injection vulnerability exploitable by high privilege users
